OL,3,CColin Todd: No split loyalties for
OL,4,CDerby County legend ahead of crucial
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FITV News Central's Mark Kielesz-Levine
OL,8,Fsat down with ex-Derby County player
OL,9,Fand manager Colin Todd ahead of
OL,10,FSaturday's big game
OL,12,FThere'll be many Rams fans who'll be
OL,13,Fglad that Colin Todd is back in the
OL,14,Farea. He may be from the North East,
OL,15,Fbut in these parts, he's very much
OL,16,Ftreated like a son of Derby and for
OL,17,Fvery good reason.
OL,19,FHe played 371 times for the club and
OL,20,Fwon two league Championships, and his
OL,21,Ffondness for the club is still there.
