OL,3,CColin Todd: No split loyalties for
OL,4,CDerby County legend ahead of crucial
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FI was welcomed into his home to
OL,8,Finterview him on 's potential
OL,9,Fpromotion and we ended up speaking
OL,10,Fabout lots of different things -
OL,11,Feverything from the footwear I had on,
OL,12,Fto his grandchildren - whom he's very
OL,13,Fproud of - and even ITV Central (yes
OL,14,Fhe watches us).
OL,16,FHe still has incredible passion and
OL,17,Fknowledge for the game, but he also
OL,18,Fdoesn't miss being part of it.
