OL,3,CColin Todd: No split loyalties for
OL,4,CDerby County legend ahead of crucial
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FThe 75-year-old started as a youth
OL,8,Fplayer at Sunderland before finding
OL,9,Fhimself at Derby and then going onto
OL,10,Fplay for, amongst others, Everton and
OL,11,FNottingham Forest.
OL,13,FMaybe uniquely, he played under Brian
OL,14,FClough at Sunderland in the youth team
OL,15,Fbriefly and also at Derby and Forest.
OL,17,FA move into management followed his
OL,18,Fplaying career and that only ended
OL,19,Feight or so years ago.
