OL,3,CColin Todd: No split loyalties for
OL,4,CDerby County legend ahead of crucial
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FIt's a lifetime in the sport and Todd
OL,8,Ffelt enough was enough - it's clear
OL,9,Fhe's enjoying life.
OL,11,FHe's moved back into Derbyshire to be
OL,12,Fnearer his son and grandchildren and
OL,13,Fvisits Pride Park when he can.
OL,15,FThe older generation will remember
OL,16,FTodd from his playing days, others
OL,17,Ffrom his time as a manager.
OL,19,FFamously he guided Bolton to the
OL,20,FPremier League, winning Division One
OL,21,Fas it was called back then, in 1997.
