OL,3,CColin Todd: No split loyalties for
OL,4,CDerby County legend ahead of crucial
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FAfter originally coming to Derby to
OL,8,Fhelp manager Jim Smith, Todd succeeded
OL,9,Fhim after Smith resigned, but the
OL,10,Fstint in the hot seat would prove to
OL,11,Fbe short lived, lasting just three
OL,12,Fmonths.
OL,14,FDerby would be relegated from the
OL,15,FPremier League that season and Todd
OL,16,Fadmitted to me that the sacking hurt,
OL,17,Fespecially the manner in which it was
OL,18,Fdone, saying it wasn't professional
OL,19,Fwith the deed being done via a phone
OL,20,Fcall on Monday morning.
