OL,3,CColin Todd: No split loyalties for
OL,4,CDerby County legend ahead of crucial
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FAnd yet, it's never soured his
OL,8,Ffeelings for the club and he certainly
OL,9,Fdoesn't hold it against Derby - far
OL,10,Ffrom it.
OL,12,FThis weekend, Bolton Wanderers will be
OL,13,Fhoping to stop Derby getting promoted,
OL,14,Fby beating Port Vale. Even with his
OL,15,Fstrong link to the Trotters, there are
OL,16,Fno split loyalties. Colin Todd wants
OL,17,FDerby to go up and described that
OL,18,Ffeeling "euphoric".
