OL,3,CColin Todd: No split loyalties for
OL,4,CDerby County legend ahead of crucial
OL,5,Cweekend
OL,7,FEven if he isn't watching them at
OL,8,FPride Park, he says the club's result
OL,9,Fis still the one he looks forward to
OL,10,Fseeing.
OL,12,FBolton may be out to ruin Derby's
OL,13,Fweekend, but the Rams need only four
OL,14,Fpoints whatever happens and they have
OL,15,FCarlisle at home in the last game of
OL,16,Fthe season.
OL,18,FColin Todd will be there amongst
OL,19,Fthousands of fans, hoping to celebrate
OL,20,Fa return to the Championship.
